The '''EOL Săcele Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Caraş-Severin County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 25 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.zf.ro/articol_176401/electrica_isi_continua_ofensiva_pe_regenerabile.html Electrica si Holrom vor construi o ferma eoliana in Judetul Constanta {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 50 MW of power, enough to power over 33,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$50 million.

